Usage: getWhatIfTimingAssertions [-help] -port <portName> [-tclList] { <blackBoxCellName>}

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>     # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                       # (string, required)
-port <portName>       # Specifies the name of one or more ports
                       # (string, required)
-tclList               # Generates the specifications as a Tcl list
                       # (bool, optional)